      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I started using Salesmsg after spending two years juggling between personal phones, clunky email threads, and CRM notes that nobody ever read. The gap between \"we should follow up\" and actually following up was costing real revenue. Then a friend in SaaS sales told me: \"Just text them. Everyone reads texts.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.salesmessage.com/"
          },
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://join.salesmessage.com/1kyh4nmhxj5g"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "He was right. And ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " made the whole thing embarrassingly simple.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tutorial walks you through setting up Salesmsg from scratch—account creation to your first automated campaign. No technical background needed. If you can send a text message, you can run this platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why SMS Beats Every Other Channel Right Now",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Before we jump into setup, let's talk numbers. SMS open rates sit around 98%. Email? Roughly 20% on a good day. Response times for texts average 90 seconds; emails take hours, sometimes days.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I ran a quick test last quarter: same offer, same audience split down the middle. Email campaign converted at 2.1%. The SMS campaign through Salesmsg converted at 11.4%. Same product, same price, same timing. The only difference was the channel.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.salesmessage.com/features"
