            "_type": "span",
            "text": "two-way texting",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", outbound calling, bulk SMS, and automation—all inside one clean interface. You're not duct-taping five tools together. It's one dashboard for your entire team.",
