      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what surprised me: the onboarding takes about three minutes. No 45-minute \"implementation calls.\" No waiting for a rep to \"provision your account.\" You sign up, verify your email, and you're inside the dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The interface greets you with a clean left sidebar: Conversations, Contacts, Campaigns, Automations, Settings. Everything labeled in plain English. I've used tools where finding the \"send a message\" button felt like solving a puzzle. Salesmsg doesn't play those games.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " During setup, Salesmsg will ask about your use case—sales, customer support, marketing, or operations. Pick the one closest to your goal. The platform tailors its default templates and automations based on your answer.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
