        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Salesmsg for both texting and calling from the same number?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Every Salesmsg plan includes a dedicated phone number that handles both SMS and voice calls. You can send texts, receive replies, and make outbound calls—all from one number. Voicemail drop is included too.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Salesmsg stay compliant with texting regulations?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg handles carrier registration, 10DLC compliance, and TCPA requirements automatically. The platform tracks opt-in consent, manages opt-outs instantly, and enforces quiet hours so messages never go out at inappropriate times.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is there a limit to how many texts I can send per campaign?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plans include monthly message credits. Basic plans cover hundreds of messages; growth plans scale to thousands or more. You can always check your usage in the dashboard and upgrade anytime with no contract lock-in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Salesmsg integrate with my existing CRM?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg offers native integrations with HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive, Close, and more. Contact data syncs bidirectionally, so your CRM stays updated with every text conversation and reply automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
